<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>go broke • go for broke</xh5><p> <i>go broke—</i>lose money and so be unable to continue in business: The paper was <u>going broke</u> and would cease publication.</p><p><i>go for broke—</i>use every possible effort; resort to extreme measures to achieve smth.: He decided to <u>go for broke</u> and put his reputation and job on the line.</p></entry>
